title: Bhaag Milkha Bhaag (2013)
summary: The truth behind the ascension of Milkha Singh who was scarred because of the India-Pakistan partition.

title: Chak de! India (2007)
summary: Kabir Khan is the coach of the Indian Women's National Hockey Team and his dream is to make his all girls team emerge victorious against all odds.

title: Munna Bhai M.B.B.S. (2003)
summary: A gangster sets out to fulfill his father's dream of becoming a doctor.
